Class SemanticAnnotation

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.fvt.opentypes.entities.SemanticAnnotation.SemanticAnnotation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SemanticAnnotation extends Object implements Serializable
SemanticAnnotation entity. A recommendation of likely mappings to Glossary Terms for all or part of an Asset.
